description: Hollywood Studios International, Inc., a media holding company, engages in the representation, production, distribution, and finance of motion pictures. The company also manages the careers of writers, directors, actors, athletes, and entertainers; produces television series; and represents writers and directors creating content for producers and studios. It also operates as a boutique agency for clients ranging from the runway to catalogues and feature films. Hollywood Studios International, Inc. was founded in 2004 and is based in Beverly Hills, California.
